    others: {"storage": "● Store below 30 ° C. ● Keep medication in its original container , tightly sealed to protect from moisture and light. ● Keep out of reach and sight of children.", "other_points": "Drug-drug/ Drug-food Interactions: ● Patients should report all prescribed medications, over-the-counter medications, traditional medicines or drinks, and health supplements, both before starting therapy and during treatment. ● They must stop taking any traditional or herbal medications, health supplements, or health drinks during treatment and should consult prescribers before starting any new medications. Vomiting Management: ● If vomiting occurs within 2 hours of dosing, an additional tablet should be taken. ● If vomiting occurs more than 2 hours after dosing, no additional dose is needed. 126"}
