    sideEffects: ["Metabolic abnormalities: Diabetes mellitus, Hyperlipidaemia, hypokalemia", "Delayed wound healing", "Increased risk of infection. Seek healthcare advice if have any symptoms of infections such as fever , chills, or flu-like symptoms.", "GI disorder: Nausea, diarrhea, vomiting, dry mouth, mouth ulcer , mucositis", "Hypertension", "Nephrotoxicity"],
