    sideEffects: ["Bloating", "Nausea & vomiting", "Breast tenderness", "Injection site reaction (bruising, pain, redness) *Note for IVF : Ovarian Hyperstimulation Syndrome (OHSS) warning signs and symptoms: Severe abdominal pain, severe nausea and vomiting, difficulty in breathing Seek help from doctor if symptoms worsen"],
    others: {"storage": "● Store at 2-8 °C (in a refrigerator). ● DO NOT FREEZE. ● Avoid storage at the door of the fridge and vegetable compartment, ensure there is proper air circulation around medication. ● TRANSPOR T of medication is only allowed in a COOL BOX WITH ICE/ICE PACKS ● Preferable return home immediately after getting medication from pharmacy to facilitate proper storage", "other_points": "NA"}
