    name: "Gamma Benzene Hexachloride, Topical",
    pharmacologicalGroup: "Topical insecticide",
    indication: "1. For topical treatment of head lice (Second-line treatment) Risk of neurologic toxicity . Should only be used in patients who cannot tolerate or have failed first-line treatment with safer medications for the treatment of scabies. To counsel based on specific medication’ s indication and dosage as prescribed by the doctor",
