    sideEffects: ["Injection site reaction (bruising, pain, redness)", "Headache Seek help from doctor if symptoms worsen"],
    others: {"storage": "1. Store at 2-8 °C (in a refrigerator). DO NOT FREEZE. Avoid storage at the door of the fridge and vegetable compartment, ensure there is proper air circulation around medication. 2. TRANSPOR T of medication is only allowed in a COOL BOX WITH ICE/ICE PACKS 3. Preferable return home immediately after getting medication from pharmacy to facilitate proper storage", "other_points": "NA"}
