    others: {"storage": "Store at room temperature.", "other_points": "1. Contraindicated in moderate or severe hepatic impairment (Child-Pugh B or C). 2. No renal dose adjustment needed for any degree of impairment. An additional dose of nevirapine should be given following dialysis."}
