    pharmacologicalGroup: "Emollients & Protectives Emollient: Fill in cracks and lines by repairing the skin barrier , helps smooth and soften skin Humectant: Attract and hold water in the top layer of skin. It increases water holding capacity of stratum corneum 1. Urea cream 10% 2. Glycerin 25% - 50% in Aqueous cream Occlusive: Repels water , also form a protective barrier to trap the moisture in the skin 1. Aqueous cream 2. Emulsifying ointment 3. White soft paraf fin + liquid paraf fin 4. White/ Yellow soft paraf fin",
